text: Shelby McEwen is an American track and field athlete who competes in the high jump. In 2019, he jumped 2.31 m indoor and then 2.30 m outdoor, as second at 2019 USA Track & Field Outdoor Championships, qualifying for the 2019 World Championships in Doha. ==References== *IAAF athlete’s profile Category:Living people Category:American male high jumpers Category:1996 births
title: Shelby McEwen
